the crazy way the ticketing agents had to go about rescheduling and tying in different carriers (United vs Air Canada, Westjet, etc.)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Only flight they have available for Halifax doesn\'t board until 3:35 PM, and arrives in Halifax at 6:10 PM.</li>\r\n 	<li>I will be missing the entire first day of the conference, but I think I can catch up.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>I made contact with my colleague (who somehow had no travel issues yesterday???) and he is sending me the items covered via email.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Spending the day in the terminal, killing time.<a href=\"http://www.donniehardin.com/personalblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/0718181428.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-102\" src=\"http://www.donniehardin.com/personalblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/0718181428.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" /></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a name=\"Wednesday, July 18, 2018 Continued\"></a>\r\n<h2>Wednesday, July 18, 2018 Continued</h2>\r\n6:15 PM (Halifax Time)\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Landed in Halifax. My coworker met me at the airport to drive me to the hotel.</li>\r\n 	<li>Checked in to room and went for dinner at a local pub\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The name of the pub was \"The Press Gang\", I learned that the owners chose this name since Halifax had a history of using Impressment to fill their naval ranks. Wikipedia article <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Impressment_(Nova_Scotia)\">here</a>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[slide-anything id=\'562\']\r\n\r\n<a name=\"Thursday, July 19, 2018\"></a>\r\n<h2>Thursday, July 19, 2018</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Second day of conference at Saint Mary\'s University. I was able to catch up on what I missed from Day 1.</li>\r\n 	<li>For dinner, we met at The Wooden Monkey (explanation of the name <a href=\"https://www.thecoast.ca/RestaurantandBarNews/archives/2014/11/06/whats-in-a-name-the-wooden-monkey\">here.</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Explored a few streets before heading back to hotel room.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[slide-anything id=\'566\']\r\n<h2>Friday, July 20, 2018</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Last day of the conference.</li>\r\n 	<li>For dinner, we met at The Henry House (history <a href=\"https://henryhouse.ca/wordpress/about-the-henry-house/\">here</a>).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[slide-anything id=\'573\']\r\n<h2>Saturday, July 21, 2018</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>To save some cash, I booked a room at Dalhousie University (They rent their open dorms to travelers during the summer months).</li>\r\n 	<li>Booked an evening harbor tour on The Tall Ship Silva.\r\n[slide-anything id=\'580\'][slide-anything id=\'577\']<span style=\"font-size: 29px; font-weight: bold;\">Sunday, July 22, 2018</span></li>\r\n 	<li>Last day in Halifax. Visited the Maritime Museum of the Atlantic.</li>\r\n 	<li>Finished the day with a tour via amphibious vehicle.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[slide-anything id=\'583\']\r\n<h2>Monday, July 23, 2018</h2>\r\n5:00 AM\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Didn\'t sleep well, decided to take an early morning walk around town.</li>\r\n 	<li>Breakfast at Tim Horton\'s.9:00 AM</li>\r\n 	<li>Took taxi to airport. Flight delayed until 12:30pm2:30 PM</li>\r\n 	<li>Arrived at Boston Logan International Airport. Connecting flight to LaGuardia delayed until approx 5:30pm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n7:30 PM\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Arrived at LaGuardia International Airport. Met connecting flight to Greensboro at 8:00</li>\r\n 	<li>10:30 PMLanded in Greensboro. Was home by 11. I was asleep before my head even hit the pillow.</li>\r\n</ul>','Halifax, Nova Scotia: July 2018','','inherit','closed','closed','','44-revision-v1','','','2018-07-25 08:50:10','2018-07-25 12:50:10','',44,'http://www.donniehardin.com/personalblog/?p=586',0,'revision','',0),(587,1,'2018-07-25 08:51:48','2018-07-25 12:51:48','I am about to take my first international trip to Halifax, Nova Scotia. Though this is a business trip, I am going to use any downtime to see and experience as much as I can. The trip will begin on T