'580\'][slide-anything id=\'577\']<span style=\"font-size: 29px; font-weight: bold;\">Sunday, July 22, 2018</span></li>\r\n 	<li>Last day in Halifax. Visited the Maritime Museum of the Atlantic.</li>\r\n 	<li>Finished the day with a tour via amphibious vehicle.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[slide-anything id=\'583\']\r\n<h2>Monday, July 23, 2018</h2>\r\n5:00 AM\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Didn\'t sleep well, decided to take an early morning walk around town.</li>\r\n 	<li>Breakfast at Tim Horton\'s.9:00 AM</li>\r\n 	<li>Took taxi to airport. Flight delayed until 12:30pm2:30 PM</li>\r\n 	<li>Arrived at Boston Logan International Airport. Connecting flight to LaGuardia delayed until approx 5:30pm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n7:30 PM\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Arrived at LaGuardia International Airport. Met connecting flight to Greensboro at 8:00</li>\r\n 	<li>10:30 PMLanded in Greensboro. Was home by 11. I was asleep before my head even hit the pillow.</li>\r\n</ul>','Halifax, Nova Scotia: July 2018','','inherit','closed','closed','','44-revision-v1','','','2018-07-25 09:02:44','2018-07-25 13:02:44','',44,'http://www.donniehardin.com/personalblog/?p=588',0,'revision','',0),(589,1,'2018-07-25 09:05:52','2018-07-25 13:05:52','I am about to take my first international trip to Halifax, Nova Scotia. Though this is a business trip, I am going to use any downtime to see and experience as much as I can. The trip will begin on Tuesday, July 17 and I will return home on Monday, July 23.\r\n<h2>Contents</h2>\r\n<a href=\"#Wednesday, June 6, 2018\">Wednesday, June 6, 2018</a>\r\n<a href=\"#Thursday, July 5, 2018\">Thursday, July 5, 2018</a>\r\n<a href=\"#Sunday, July 15, 2018\">Sunday, July 15, 2018</a>\r\n<a href=\"#Monday, July 16, 2018\">Monday, July 16, 2018</a>\r\n<a href=\"#Tuesday, July 17, 2018\">Tuesday, July 17, 2018</a>\r\n<a href=\"#Wednesday, July 18, 2018\">Wednesday, July 18, 2018</a>\r\n<a href=\"#Wednesday, July 18, 2018 Continued\">Wednesday, July 18, 2018 Continued</a>\r\n<a href=\"#Thursday, July 19, 201